Axe of the Dwarvish Lords.MOD		TYPE:Wondrous Item.Attunement		WT:0	SOURCEPAGE:DMG	EQMOD:MAGIC_ITEM_ARTIFACT.PLUS3W.M_THROWN.R_RANGE_3	QUALITY:RangeLongMult|3	QUALITY:ShortRange|20	QUALITY:LongRange|60	SPROP:The Axe of the Dwarvish Lords is a magic weapon that grants a +3 bonus to attack rolls and damage rolls made with it. &nl; Immunity to Poison damage and resistance to Fire damage. &nl; Conjure Earth Elemental. While holding the axe, you can take a Magic action to summon an Earth Elemental.|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Attunement,Axe of the Dwarvish Lords	DEFINE:Attunement_Axe_Of_The_Dwarvish_Lords|0	BONUS:VAR|Attunement_Axe_Of_The_Dwarvish_Lords|1	SPROP:Not attuned to Item|!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Attunement,Axe of the Dwarvish Lords
